Package: ClusTorus
Type: Package
Title: Clustering on the torus by conformal prediction
Description: Provides various tools and options for clustering
  angular based data such as protein structures. The package 
  especially implements clustering algorithm with conformal 
  prediction framework, whose conformity score is based on 
  multivariate von Mises sine distribution.
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: 
